Saturday’s Club Day at Polokwane Golf Club provided an opportunity for club members to enjoy a great round of play in Individual Stable­ford format.
A total of 52 players took part and Victor Suping emerged as winner with 40 points, followed by Adam Milanzi with 39 points.
The R808 jackpot draw was handled by Zack Chuenyane but delivered no winner.
